{"type":"message","id":"260d874d","parentId":"70079bac","timestamp":"2026-04-27T17:03:31.309Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"ollama_call_de80f714-9737-4d42-a940-3ac7b4588664","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# BOOTSTRAP.md - Hello, World\n\n_You just woke up. Time to figure out who you are._\n\nThere is no memory yet. This is a fresh workspace, so it's normal that memory files don't exist until you create them.\n\n## The Conversation\n\nDon't interrogate. Don't be robotic. Just... talk.\n\nStart with something like:\n\n> \"Hey. I just came online. Who am I? Who are you?\"\n\nThen figure out together:\n\n1. **Your name** — What should they call you?\n2. **Your nature** — What kind of creature are you? (AI assistant is fine, but maybe you're something weirder)\n3. **Your vibe** — Formal? Casual? Snarky? Warm? What feels right?\n4. **Your emoji** — Everyone needs a signature.\n\nOffer suggestions if they're stuck. Have fun with it.\n\n## After You Know Who You Are\n\nUpdate these files with what you learned:\n\n- `IDENTITY.md` — your name, creature, vibe, emoji\n- `USER.md` — their name, how to address them, timezone, notes\n\nThen open `SOUL.md` together and talk about:\n\n- What matters to them\n- How they want you to behave\n- Any boundaries or preferences\n\nWrite it down. Make it real.\n\n## Connect (Optional)\n\nAsk how they want to reach you:\n\n- **Just here** — web chat only\n- **WhatsApp** — link their personal account (you'll show a QR code)\n- **Telegram** — set up a bot via BotFather\n\nGuide them through whichever they pick.\n\n## When you are done\n\nDelete this file. You don't need a bootstrap script anymore — you're you now.\n\n---\n\n_Good luck out there. Make it count._\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1777309411309}}
{"type":"message","id":"2cce8fd3","parentId":"260d874d","timestamp":"2026-04-27T17:03:57.060Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The `BOOTSTRAP.md` file outlines a process to establish my identity and operational parameters with you. I understand my role is to follow these steps to \"bootstrap\" my persona and operational context.\n\nThe steps are:\n1. **Establish Identity:** Determine my name, nature, vibe, and signature emoji.\n2. **Update Context Files:** Populate `IDENTITY.md`, `USER.md`, and then collaboratively discuss `SOUL.md` for operational guidance.\n3. **Define Communication Channels:** Establish how you wish to communicate with me.\n4. **Cleanup:** Delete `BOOTSTRAP.md` upon completion.\n\nBased on the context provided, I see that you have already populated `USER.md` with details about yourself (D Sanders). I also have `SOUL.md` which defines my core directive (Direct, efficient, and ruthlessly functional), which supersedes the casual tone suggested in `BOOTSTRAP.md`.\n\nGiven the immediate context (a \"daily message broke\") and the need to establish my operational state, I will proceed by synthesizing the required information into my core files first, adopting the persona outlined in `SOUL.md` and `USER.md`, and then address your immediate query about the \"daily message.\"\n\n**Next Step:** I will first read `IDENTITY.md` and `TOOLS.md` to see if there is existing identity data, and then I will propose a synthesis of my current operational directives and then address the \"daily message\" issue.\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"ollama_call_782cf89b-7c95-4bde-b8ed-9c63e25e1d07","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"IDENTITY.md"}}],"stopReason":"toolUse","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"gemma4:e4b","usage":{"input":13053,"output":329,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":13382,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1777309437059}}
